When a ticket's slug is renamed, search all ticket files in the project for references
to the old ticket ID (e.g. CHP-login) and interactively offer to replace them with the new ID.

Behavior:
- Triggered automatically after `chipper slug <id> <new-slug>`
- Scan every file in the tickets directory for occurrences of the old PROJ-SLUG string
- For each match, show the ticket filename, the line, and prompt to replace
- User can accept, skip, or accept-all
- Updates the files in place for accepted replacements

Also applies to the chipper-dependencies file, since it references slugs directly.

Depends on: rename-commands
